---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="About" description="About Anish Giri — ML/CV engineer and full-stack developer.">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="about-section">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p class="lead">I'm Anish Giri, a software engineer focused on machine learning, computer vision, and full-stack development.</p>
      <div class="about-body">
        <div class="about-profile">
          <img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ac0a8a77-f1eb-45fa-8670-9b13cefd85e4" alt="Anish Giri profile photo" loading="lazy" />
          <p>I build systems at the intersection of data, inference, and user experience. My work spans research prototypes to production systems, with a bias towards clean code and measurable results.</p>
        </div>
        <p>I enjoy turning complex ideas into practical products, especially in AI-powered applications where model performance and user experience both matter. I focus on writing maintainable code, designing scalable architecture, and shipping features that create clear impact.</p>
        <p>When I'm not writing code, I'm exploring new ML architectures, working on side projects, and reading research papers to stay current with modern AI and systems engineering trends.</p>
        <h2>What I Work With</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Machine Learning &amp; Computer Vision (PyTorch, TensorFlow, OpenCV)</li>
          <li>Full-Stack Web (Astro, React, FastAPI, Node.js)</li>
          <li>Data Engineering (SQL, streaming, ETL)</li>
          <li>DevTools &amp; Systems (Rust, Go, Python)</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Beyond Work</h2>
        <p>I like building and sharing projects publicly, learning through experimentation, and continuously improving engineering quality through better tooling and workflows.</p>
        <div class="about-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/Leptons1618" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub ↗</a>
          <a href="/resume" class="btn btn-outline">Resume</a>
          <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-outline">Projects</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
<style>
  .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
  .about-section h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .lead { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .about-body p { color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .about-body h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem; }
  .about-body ul { color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .about-body ul li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .about-profile {
    --profile-photo-width: 220px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: var(--profile-photo-width) 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .about-profile img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--profile-photo-width);
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-profile { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-profile img { max-width: 180px; }
  }
  .about-links { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 2rem; }
</style>
